content: sinecose: Merged 3 significant PRs this month, focusing on logger replacements and import cleanup across multiple plugins. Notable contributions include PR #1888 for replacing console with elizaLogger in the Solana plugin (+29257/-8620 lines) and PR #1744 for removing unused imports in the Cronos ZKEVM plugin (+44980/-41377 lines). Modified a substantial 1,240 files with over 42K additions and 41K deletions across 8 commits, showing sporadic activity on just 3 days this month.
